msgstr "Largas Noches de Oficina"

#: data/levels/revenge_in_redmond/outro.stl:3
msgid "Where Is Everyone?"
msgstr "¿Dónde están todos?"

#: data/levels/revenge_in_redmond/outro.txt:4
msgid ""
"-Where Is Everyone?\n"
"\n"
"\tTux ran into the castle's throne room,\n"
"\tfrantically searching for the penguin girl Gown.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tAlas, he found neither Gown, nor the pilot\n"
"\tof the helicopter there, but instead, a statue.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tIt depicted a scaly creature with crossed arms.\n"
"\tThe pedestal it resided on was inscribed\n"
"\twith the word \"Nolok\". Was it a name?\n"
"\t\n"
"\tHe was unsure who or what\n"
"\tthis statue was depicting.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tAll of a sudden, Tux remembered...\n"
"\t\n"
"\tHe and Penny were ambushed\n"
"\tby this exact creature,\n"
"\tduring their picnic on the ice fields!\n"
"\t\n"
"\tTux opened his eyes. He was back\n"
"\tat the ice fields near the shore.\n"
"\tPenny, however, was gone.\n"
"\tShocked by this, he began looking around,\n"
"\tbut all he could find was a note...\n"
"\t\n"
"\t...from Nolok.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"-The End\n"
" Or rather, the beginning...?"
msgstr ""
"¿Dónde Está Todo el Mundo?\n"
"\n"
"\tTux corrió a la sala del trono del castillo, \n"
"\tbuscando frenéticamente a la chica pingüino Gown.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tPor desgracia, no encontró ni a Gown, ni al piloto \n"
"\tdel helicóptero, sino una estatua.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tRepresentaba a una criatura escamosa con los brazos cruzados.\n"
"\tEl pedestal en el que se encontraba tenía inscrita \n"
"\tcon la palabra \"Nolok\". ¿Era un nombre?\n"
"\t\n"
"\tNo estaba seguro de a quién o qué \n"
"\trepresentaba la estatua.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tDe repente, Tux recordó...\n"
"\t\n"
"\tÉl y Penny fueron emboscados \n"
"\tpor esta misma criatura, \n"
"\t¡durante su picnic en los campos de hielo!\n"
"\t\n"
"\tTux abrió los ojos. Estaba de vuelta \n"
"\ten los campos de hielo cerca de la orilla.\n"
"\tSin embargo, Penny se había ido.\n"
"\tSorprendido, comenzó a mirar a su alrededor,\n"
"\tpero lo único que encontró fue una nota...\n"
"\t\n"
"\t...de Nolok.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"El Fin\n"
"¿O mejor dicho, el inicio...?"

